# Student-SpendTrack
##Project Overview
  Many students run out of balance before the end of the week because they don’t track where their money goes. The problem is they don’t have simple way to track big or small expenses. Our proposed system solution is the Student SpendTrack where students can quickly log what they buy and see how many money they have left.

##Data Structure and Algorithm used.
Data structure: [Array, Linked List, and Hash Table]
Algorithms: [Search and sort]
